create SCHEMA dwh_schema go 

CREATE TABLE dwh_schema.trip_data_repoting
WITH
(
    DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN,
    CLUSTERED COLUMNSTORE INDEX
)as

GO


select * from dwh_schema.trip_data_repoting;


CREATE TABLE dwh_schema.trip_data_analysis
WITH
(
    DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN,
    CLUSTERED COLUMNSTORE INDEX
)as 
select * from staging.tripdata
GO

select * from dwh_schema.trip_data_analysis;
